{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"1਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਸੂਰਜ ਨੂੰ ਵਲੇਟ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।1","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1 ਵੇਖੋ ਸੂਰਤ ਅਲ-ਕਯਾਮਾ, ਹਾਸ਼ੀਆ ਆਇਤ 9/75","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā al-shamsu kuwwirat ","translations":["When","the sun","is wrapped up","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","al-shamsu","kuwwirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,1290],[3,1290,2355]]}},{"name":"81:2","price":"2਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਤਾਰੇ ਬੇ-ਨੂਰ ਹੋ ਜਾਣਗੇ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-nujūmu inkadarat ","translations":["And when","the stars","fall, losing their luster","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-nujūmu","inkadarat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,2060],[3,2060,3665]]}},{"name":"81:3","price":"3਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਪਹਾੜਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਤੋਰਿਆ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jibālu suyyirat ","translations":["And when","the mountains","are moved away","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jibālu","suyyirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1670],[3,1670,2705]]}},{"name":"81:4","price":"4਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਦਸ-ਦਸ ਮਹੀਨਿਆਂ ਦੀਆਂ ਗਭਣ ਊਂਠਣੀਆਂ ਨੂੰ ਐਵੇਂ ਖੁੱਲ੍ਹਾ ਹੀ ਛੱਡ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-ʿishāru ʿuṭṭilat ","translations":["And when","the full-term she-camels","(are) left untended","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-ʿishāru","ʿuṭṭilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,1850],[3,1850,2775]]}},{"name":"81:5","price":"5਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਜੰਗਲੀ ਜਾਨਵਰਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਇਕੱਤਰਤ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","ar