ਧੂ ਸਵਾਲ ਕਰਨਾ ਤੇ 3਼ ਦੌਲਤ ਦੇ ਬਰਬਾਦ ਕਰਨ ਨੂੰ। (ਸਹੀ ਬੁਖ਼ਾਰੀ, ਹਦੀਸ: 2408)","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-mawūdatu su-ilat ","translations":["And when","the female infant buried alive","is asked","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-mawūdatu","su-ilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,2070],[3,2070,2955]]}},{"name":"81:9","price":"9਼ ਕਿ ਉਸ ਨੂੰ ਕਿਸ ਦੋਸ਼ ਵਿਚ ਮਾਰਿਆ ਗਿਆ ਸੀ ?","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-ayyi dhanbin qutilat ","translations":["For what","sin","she was killed","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-ayyi","dhanbin","qutilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2670],[3,2670,4175]]}},{"name":"81:10","price":"10਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਕਰਮ-ਪੱਤਰ ਖੋਲੇ ਜਾਣਗੇ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-ṣuḥufu nushirat ","translations":["And when","the pages","are laid open","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-ṣuḥufu","nushirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1360],[3,1360,2195]]}},{"name":"81:11","price":"11਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਅਕਾਸ਼ ਦੀ ਖੱਲ (ਪੜਦਾ) ਉਤਾਰ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-samāu kushiṭat ","translations":["And when","the sky","is stripped away","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-samāu","kushiṭat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,2980],[3,2980,3775]]}},{"name":"81:12","price":"12਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਨਰਕ (ਅੱਗ ਨਾਲ) ਭੜਕਾਈ ਜਾਵੇਗੀ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jaḥīmu suʿʿirat ","translations":["And when","th