ਹੈ। (ਸਹੀ ਮੁਸਲਿਮ, ਹਦੀਸ: 153)","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"in huwa illā dhik'run lil'ʿālamīna ","translations":["Not","it","(is) except","a reminder","to the worlds","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["in","huwa","illā","dhik'run","lil'ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,800],[3,800,1670],[4,1670,2300],[5,2300,5255]]}},{"name":"81:28","price":"28਼ (ਪਰ ਇਹ ਉਸ ਲਈ ਹੈ) ਜਿਹੜਾ ਤੁਹਾਡੇ ’ਚੋਂ ਸਿੱਧੇ ਰਾਹ ਤੁਰਨਾ ਚਾਹੁੰਦਾ ਹੈ।","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"liman shāa minkum an yastaqīma ","translations":["For whoever","wills","among you","to","take a straight way","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["liman","shāa","minkum","an","yastaqīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1520],[2,1520,3140],[3,3140,4340],[4,4340,4640],[5,4640,8225]]}},{"name":"81:29","price":"29਼ ਅਤੇ ਕੁਲ ਜਹਾਨ ਦੇ ਪਾਲਣਹਾਰ ਦੇ ਚਾਹਨ ਤੋਂ ਬਿਨਾਂ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਕੁਝ ਨਹੀਂ ਕਰ ਸਕਦੇ।","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā tashāūna illā an yashāa al-lahu rabbu al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["And not","you will","except","that","wills","Allah","Lord","(of) the worlds","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","tashāūna","illā","an","yashāa","al-lahu","rabbu","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,3030],[3,3030,4560],[4,4560,4990],[5,4990,6970],[6,6970,8110],[7,8110,8700],[8,8700,12375]]}}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"],"version":{"key":"punjabi_arif","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"pa","version":"1.0.0","last_update":1666783255,"title":"Punjabi translation","description":"Translation